What you need to know:  Shujaa will then renew their rivalry with Sydney Sevens bronze medal winners Fiji, who are yet to win any leg this season at 1.18am on Sunday before wrapping up against Japan at 4.37am the same dayIt will be the second time Kenya is facing Australia this season after the two sides battled to a 19-19 draw at Dubai Sevens in DecemberKenya Sevens head coach Damian McGrath has handed Strathmore Leos half back Brunson Madigu his Series debut besides recalling Mwamba duo of Billy Odhiambo and Daniel Taabu